{"type": "article", "id": 25004, "title": "可3D打印零件的电动自行车", "description": "", "date": "2016-04-06T07:18:58Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 17, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607104114ACITxoBaN8DZWum6.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这辆电动自行车的零件可以 3D 打印，它允许用户自己在网站上下载文件打印零件以更换。这些零件包括后挡泥板、挡泥板支架和前制动闸等结构，而它的主要结构是用铝合金做的，与原本轻盈的结构对比，看起来很酷，它也有提高行驶速度的功能。内有 42V 锂离子供电，3 小时充电后可行驶 97 公里。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104111zocakxCE4vNSiYZ7.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071041120BN9wiF5lzaHkdof.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104112c7BgS9UDOQbMjufK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104113Jyi6Adhm2bwWfep5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66503667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104113yRt1vH4lXG6jwPKe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}